            "body": "Was able to reproduce and device a minimal reproducer:\n```lua\n-- test.lua\nlocal ns = vim.api.nvim_create_namespace('')\nvim.cmd('call setline(1, range(1, 2))')\nvim.o.signcolumn = 'auto:2'\nvim.api.nvim_buf_set_extmark(0, ns, 0, 0, { sign_text = 'S', invalidate = true, end_row = 0 })\nvim.api.nvim_buf_set_extmark(0, ns, 1, 0, { sign_text = 'S', end_row = 1 })\nvim.keymap.set('n', 'X', function()\n  vim.api.nvim_buf_clear_namespace(0, ns, 0, -1)\nend, {})\n-- build/bin/nvim --clean -S test.lua\n-- type \"ddX\"\n```\n\nNow to find and fix the problem...",
